author: RTÉ News
title: Tiger at Bronx Zoo tests positive for Covid-19
description: A tiger at New York's Bronx Zoo has tested positive for COVID-19 and it is believed to have contracted the virus from a caretaker who was asymptomatic at the time.
content:
A tiger at New York's Bronx Zoo has tested positive for COVID-19, the institution said over the weekend.
It is believed to have contracted the virus from a caretaker who was asymptomatic at the time.
